Method Path Description <code>GET</code> <code>/management/v1/health</code> Overall system health: gateway, orchestrator, state store <code>GET</code> <code>/management/v1/health/providers</code> Per-provider reachability and latency <code>GET</code> <code>/management/v1/metrics</code> Prometheus-compatible metrics scrape endpoint <p><code>GET /management/v1/health</code> response:</p> <pre><code>{
  "ok": true,
  "data": {
    "status": "degraded",
    "components": {
      "gateway":      { "status": "ok",      "latency_ms": 1 },
      "orchestrator": { "status": "ok",      "latency_ms": 3 },
      "state_store":  { "status": "ok",      "latency_ms": 8 },
      "redis":        { "status": "degraded","latency_ms": 420, "message": "high latency" }
    },
    "checked_at": "2026-04-12T10:00:00Z"
  }
}
</code></pre> <p>Overall <code>status</code> is <code>"ok"</code> only if all components are <code>"ok"</code>. Otherwise <code>"degraded"</code> or <code>"down"</code>.</p>

Method Path Description <code>GET</code> <code>/management/v1/usage</code> Aggregated token/request usage across all accounts <code>GET</code> <code>/management/v1/usage/accounts/:id</code> Per-account usage time series <code>GET</code> <code>/management/v1/usage/sessions/:id</code> Per-session token consumption breakdown <code>GET</code> <code>/management/v1/events</code> Live event stream (SSE) of system events <code>GET</code> <code>/management/v1/audit</code> Paginated audit log of all management mutations <p><code>GET /management/v1/events</code> (SSE):</p> <p>The events stream is used by the dashboard for live updates. Each event has a <code>type</code> and <code>data</code> payload:</p> <pre><code>event: session.status_changed
data: {"session_id":"abc123","old_status":"active","new_status":"dirty","ts":"2026-04-12T10:01:00Z"}

event: account.cooldown_entered
data: {"account_id":"acct_01","provider":"codex","reason":"429","ts":"2026-04-12T10:01:05Z"}

event: provider.health_changed
data: {"provider":"gemini","old_status":"ok","new_status":"degraded","ts":"2026-04-12T10:01:10Z"}
</code></pre> <p>Event types:</p> Event Type Trigger <code>session.created</code> New session registered <code>session.status_changed</code> Session status transitions <code>session.terminated</code> Session deleted by operator <code>account.cooldown_entered</code> Account received 429 <code>account.cooldown_exited</code> Account cooldown expired <code>account.registered</code> New account added to pool <code>provider.health_changed</code> Provider reachability status change <code>orchestrator.semaphore_full</code> Global concurrency limit reached
